{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852786074,"sessionID":"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9","part":{"id":"prt_d79130e95001CMopJ0JeToGaXy","messageID":"msg_d7912f3cf001iJ5mC7imrcQmRx","sessionID":"ses_286ed4f0bffefmfnGF4OM7xCV9","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-8a6b54aca815436ba2ba4676b15c1cf7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-012/CHANGE.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-012/CHANGE.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 ŌĆö õ╝ÜĶ»ØÕŁśÕé©µÄźÕÅŻÕ«Üõ╣ē\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: - **AR**: AR-012\n5: - **Title**: õ╝ÜĶ»ØÕŁśÕé©µÄźÕÅŻÕ«Üõ╣ē\n6: - **Module**: pkg/store\n7: - **Language**: Go\n8: - **Size**: S\n9: - **Status**: Pending\n10: \n11: ## Description\n12: Define the session storage interface for the AgentCube project.\n13: \n14: ## Dependencies\n15: None\n16: \n17: ## Related Changes\n18: None\n\n(End of file - total 18 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 ŌĆö õ╝ÜĶ»ØÕŁśÕé©µÄźÕÅŻÕ«Üõ╣ē\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-012\n- **Title**: õ╝ÜĶ»ØÕŁśÕé©µÄźÕÅŻÕ«Üõ╣ē\n- **Module**: pkg/store\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\nDefine the session storage interface for the AgentCube project.\n\n## Dependencies\nNone\n\n## Related Changes\nNone","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-012/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775852786037,"end":1775852786072}}}}
